OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FOnce low cloud clears in the
OL,6,Fnortheast, it will be a fine, settled
OL,7,Fday ahead with lots of sunshine.
OL,8,FCloudier in parts of the southwest
OL,9,Fwith some spells of rain in Cornwall.
OL,10,FStill rather windy. Warm. Cooler along
OL,11,Fwindward coasts.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FSome rain in the southwest
OL,14,Fand parts of Wales and Northern
OL,15,FIreland. Otherwise a dry and clear
OL,16,Fnight. Chilly in the northeast. A warm
OL,17,Fnight in the south and west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
