OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FShowers in the west and
OL,6,Fsouthwest will spread northeastwards.
OL,7,FTurning heavy in places with some
OL,8,Fthundery bursts. Feeling much warmer
OL,9,Fin the east with some sunshine. Humid
OL,10,Fin the south.
